# The Python-build-artifact `lib/` rule above also matches the SPA's pages/src/lib
# directory; re-include it so its source and tests (e.g. pages/src/lib/__tests__/)
# are tracked and run in CI, not silently ignored.
!pages/src/lib/
!pages/src/lib/**
